<plot>Two college-aged guys named Mario and Luigi are walking down a suburban street chatting. One picks up a cap and puts it on. Suddenly, one of the guys has disappeared and the one in the hat finds himself in a life-sized, live Super Mario Brothers game with things to jump over, bricks to break, holes to jump into, and problems to dodge. His score is at the top of the screen. How will he do?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?652675</url></doc>
